### 1. Login Agent (obtenir token)
POST http://localhost/collectepro/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "agent1@express.cm",
  "mot_de_passe": "Agent1234"
}

###

### 2. Dashboard Agent (remplacer TOKEN_ICI par le token reçu)
GET http://localhost/collectepro/api/agent/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_ICI

###

### 3. Clients de l'agent
GET http://localhost/collectepro/api/agent/clients
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_ICI

###

### 4. Commissions de l'agent
GET http://localhost/collectepro/api/agent/commissions
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_ICI

###
